%spark
import org.apache.commons.io.IOUtils
import java.net.URL
import java.nio.charset.Charset
import java.text.SimpleDateFormat
import java.util.Calendar
import java.sql.Date
import java.sql.Timestamp
println("""%html <b> Pended Claim missing from Facets workflow(False positive) """)
val claimstbldt="file:///C:/Users/224597/Documents/CLAIMS/DATA/claims_not_inwf_not_inlk_1004.csv"
val claimstbldt_xc="file:///C:/Users/224597/Documents/CLAIMS/DATA/claims_not_inwf_not_inlk_XC_1004.csv"

def getDate(x:Any) : Date = {
    val format = new SimpleDateFormat("yyyy-MM-dd")
    if (x.toString() == "") 
    return null
    else {
        val d = format.parse(x.toString());
        return new java.sql.Date(d.getTime())
    }
}

val non_xc = sc.parallelize(IOUtils.toString(new URL(claimstbldt),Charset.forName("utf8")).split("\n"))
val xc = sc.parallelize(IOUtils.toString(new URL(claimstbldt_xc),Charset.forName("utf8")).split("\n"))
case class missing_in_wf(CLAIMS:String , DATE_OF_CLAIMS:java.sql.Date , CLAIM_STS:String ,Type :String)

val claims_non_xc = non_xc.map(s=>s.split(",")).filter(s=>s(0)!="\"COUNT_OF_CLAIMS\"").map(
    s=>missing_in_wf(
        s(0).replaceAll("\"", ""), 
        getDate(s(1)),
        s(2).replaceAll("\"", ""),
        "non-XC"
        )
)
val claims_xc = xc.map(s=>s.split(",")).filter(s=>s(0)!="\"COUNT_OF_CLAIMS\"").map(
    s=>missing_in_wf(
        s(0).replaceAll("\"", ""), 
        getDate(s(1)),
        s(2).replaceAll("\"", ""),
        "XC"
        )
)
claims_non_xc.toDF().registerTempTable("claimsNonXc")
claims_xc.toDF().registerTempTable("claimsXc")
var nonxc_claims_result= claims_non_xc.toDF().sqlContext.sql(s"select count(CLAIMS) as CLAIM_COUNT,Type,DATE_OF_CLAIMS FROM claimsNonXc GROUP BY DATE_OF_CLAIMS,Type order by DATE_OF_CLAIMS")
var xc_claim_result= claims_xc.toDF().sqlContext.sql(s"select count(CLAIMS) as CLAIM_COUNT ,Type,DATE_OF_CLAIMS FROM claimsXc GROUP BY DATE_OF_CLAIMS,Type order by DATE_OF_CLAIMS")
val result_df = nonxc_claims_result.unionAll(xc_claim_result)
val result_df_1 =result_df.orderBy($"DATE_OF_CLAIMS".asc)
z.show(result_df_1)

%spark
import java.net.URL
import java.nio.charset.Charset
import java.text.SimpleDateFormat
import java.util.Calendar
import java.sql.Date
import java.sql.Timestamp
println("""%html <b> Claims which are accepted and awaiting batch ,struck in Facets workflow(False negative)
""")

var clcl_start_date=getDate(z.input("Claims start date", "2018-01-01"))
var clcl_end_date=getDate(z.input("Claims end date", "2019-01-01"))
val claims_not_in_core = sc.parallelize(IOUtils.toString(new URL("file:///C:/Users/224597/Documents/CLAIMS/DATA/cliams_in_wf_not_in_claim_tbl_1004.csv"),Charset.forName("utf8")).split("\n"))

case class wf_frame(WQMS_MESSAGE_ID:String ,WQMS_PRIORITY:String,WQMS_STATUS:String,WQMS_RECEIVED_DT :java.sql.Date )
val wf_details = claims_not_in_core.map(s=>s.split(",")).map(
    s=>wf_frame(
        s(0).replaceAll("\"", ""), 
        s(1).replaceAll("\"", ""), 
        s(2).replaceAll("\"", ""), 
        getDate(s(3))
        )
)
wf_details.toDF().registerTempTable("wf_details_df")
var wf_result= wf_details.toDF().sqlContext.sql(s"SELECT count(WQMS_MESSAGE_ID) as COUNT_OF_CLAIMS,WQMS_PRIORITY  , WQMS_RECEIVED_DT from wf_details_df where WQMS_RECEIVED_DT >='$clcl_start_date' and  WQMS_RECEIVED_DT <= '$clcl_end_date'   GROUP BY WQMS_PRIORITY, WQMS_RECEIVED_DT ORDER BY WQMS_RECEIVED_DT")
z.show(wf_result)

%spark
import java.net.URL
import java.nio.charset.Charset
import java.text.SimpleDateFormat
import java.util.Calendar
import java.sql.Date
import java.sql.Timestamp
println("""%html <b> Claims Drag date Analytics  (False Positive) """)

var clcl_start_date=getDate(z.input("Claims start date", "2018-01-01"))
var clcl_end_date=getDate(z.input("Claims end date", "2019-01-01"))
val dragdt_past = sc.parallelize(IOUtils.toString(new URL("file:///C:/Users/224597/Documents/CLAIMS/DATA/claims_drag_dt_with_25dy_1004.csv"),Charset.forName("utf8")).split("\n"))
val dragdt_1753 = sc.parallelize(IOUtils.toString(new URL("file:///C:/Users/224597/Documents/CLAIMS/DATA/claims_drag_dt_with_1753_1004.csv"),Charset.forName("utf8")).split("\n"))

case class drag_dt_frame(CLAIM_ID:String ,DRAG_DT :java.sql.Date,REASON:String ,RECIEVED_DT:java.sql.Date,Type:String)
val dragdt_past_data = dragdt_past.map(s=>s.split(",")).map(
    s=>drag_dt_frame(
        s(0).replaceAll("\"", ""), 
        getDate(s(1)),
        s(2).replaceAll("\"", ""),
        getDate(s(3)),
        "Have Drag date"
        )
)
val dragdt_1753_data = dragdt_1753.map(s=>s.split(",")).map(
    s=>drag_dt_frame(
        s(0).replaceAll("\"", ""), 
        getDate(s(1)),
       s(2).replaceAll("\"", ""),
        getDate(s(3)),
        "1753 Drag date"
        )
)
dragdt_past_data.toDF().registerTempTable("past_drag_dt")
dragdt_1753_data.toDF().registerTempTable("1753_drag_dt")
var drag_past_result= dragdt_past_data.toDF().sqlContext.sql(s"Select count(CLAIM_ID) as NUMBER_OF_CLAIMS ,DRAG_DT , REASON ,RECIEVED_DT ,Type from past_drag_dt WHERE RECIEVED_DT >='$clcl_start_date' and RECIEVED_DT <='$clcl_end_date' GROUP BY DRAG_DT , REASON ,RECIEVED_DT ,Type")
var drag_1753_result= dragdt_past_data.toDF().sqlContext.sql(s"Select count(CLAIM_ID) AS NUMBER_OF_CLAIMS ,DRAG_DT , REASON ,RECIEVED_DT ,Type from 1753_drag_dt WHERE RECIEVED_DT >='$clcl_start_date' and RECIEVED_DT <='$clcl_end_date' GROUP BY DRAG_DT , REASON ,RECIEVED_DT ,Type")
var drag_past_result_new=drag_past_result.union(drag_1753_result)
val drag_past_result_new_1 =drag_past_result_new.orderBy($"RECIEVED_DT".asc)
z.show(drag_past_result_new_1)

%spark
import java.net.URL
import java.nio.charset.Charset
import java.text.SimpleDateFormat
import java.util.Calendar
import java.sql.Date
import java.sql.Timestamp
println("""%html <b> Claims Ready for payment but no check issued (False Positive) """)

var clcl_start_date=getDate(z.input("Claims start date", "2018-01-01"))
var clcl_end_date=getDate(z.input("Claims end date", "2019-01-01"))
val claims_no_check = sc.parallelize(IOUtils.toString(new URL("file:///C:/Users/224597/Documents/CLAIMS/DATA/claims_with_no_check_1004.csv"),Charset.forName("utf8")).split("\n"))
case class claims_no_checkdf(CLAIM_ID:String ,RECEIVED_DT :java.sql.Date,CLAIM_AMT:String)
val claims_no_check_df = claims_no_check.map(s=>s.split(",")).map(
    s=>claims_no_checkdf(
        s(0).replaceAll("\"", ""), 
       getDate(s(1)),
         s(2).replaceAll("\"", "")
        )
)

claims_no_check_df.toDF().registerTempTable("claims_no_checks")
var claims_no_check_result= claims_no_check_df.toDF().sqlContext.sql(s"SELECT count(CLAIM_ID) as COUNT_OF_CLAIMS ,RECEIVED_DT FROM  claims_no_checks WHERE RECEIVED_DT >='$clcl_start_date' and RECEIVED_DT <='$clcl_end_date' GROUP BY RECEIVED_DT ORDER BY RECEIVED_DT")

z.show(claims_no_check_result)
